{"id":2542,"date":"2022-02-22T15:01:12","date_gmt":"2022-02-22T08:01:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2542"},"modified":"2023-09-18T15:04:26","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T08:04:26","slug":"thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-lien-thong-dai-hoc-cao-dang-chinh-quy-dot-1-nam-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-lien-thong-dai-hoc-cao-dang-chinh-quy-dot-1-nam-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O TUY\u1ec2N SINH LI\u00caN TH\u00d4NG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC, CAO \u0110\u1eb2NG CH\u00cdNH QUY \u0110\u1ee2T 1 N\u0102M 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>TR<\/strong><strong>\u01af\u1edcNG<\/strong><strong> \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4 TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O TUY\u1ec2N SINH LI\u00caN TH\u00d4NG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC, CAO \u0110\u1eb2NG CH\u00cdNH QUY \u0110\u1ee2T 1 N\u0102M 2022<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh li\u00ean th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, cao \u0111\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ee3t 1 n\u0103m 2022 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong> \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh:<\/strong><br \/>\n&#8211; Th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p trung c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/li>\n<li><strong> Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c, ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong><em>2.1. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT: T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 3 m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a 03 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 (2 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 l\u1edbp 11v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 1 l\u1edbp 12) ho\u1eb7c n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 + \u0111i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb <strong>16 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong> tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Thi tuy\u1ec3n 3 m\u00f4n: C\u01a1 b\u1ea3n; C\u01a1 s\u1edf ng\u00e0nh; Chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o<\/p>\n<p><strong><em>2.2. Ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>TT<\/td>\n<td><strong>Ng\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>T\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><strong>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc li\u00ean th\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh quy<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1<\/td>\n<td>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">A00, A01, D01, D07<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2<\/td>\n<td>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt\u00a0 \u00d4 t\u00f4<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0110i\u1ec7n, \u0110i\u1ec7n t\u1eed<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td>K\u1ebf to\u00e1n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kinh doanh<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">A00, A01,C00, D01<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6<\/td>\n<td>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7<\/td>\n<td>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8<\/td>\n<td>Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9<\/td>\n<td>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Anh<\/td>\n<td>D01, D07, D14, D15<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<td>D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc (C\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129)<\/td>\n<td>A00, A11, B00, D07<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><strong>Cao \u0111\u1eb3ng li\u00ean th\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh quy<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1<\/td>\n<td>Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2<\/td>\n<td>Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn du l\u1ecbch<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td>Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td>D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><strong><em>2.3. T\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>A00: <\/strong>To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, H\u00f3a<\/td>\n<td><strong>B00:<\/strong> To\u00e1n, H\u00f3a, Sinh<\/td>\n<td><strong>D07:<\/strong> To\u00e1n, H\u00f3a, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>A01: <\/strong>To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/td>\n<td><strong>C00:<\/strong> V\u0103n, S\u1eed, \u0110\u1ecba<\/td>\n<td><strong>D14:<\/strong> V\u0103n, S\u1eed, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>A11:<\/strong> To\u00e1n, H\u00f3a, GDCD<\/td>\n<td><strong>D01: <\/strong>To\u00e1n, V\u0103n, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/td>\n<td><strong>D15:<\/strong> V\u0103n, \u0110\u1ecba, Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong> Th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp to\u00e0n kh\u00f3a:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong><em>3.1. \u00a0Th\u1eddi gian:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><em>&#8211; Nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1: <\/em>T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>18\/<\/strong><strong>02<\/strong><strong>\/202<\/strong><strong>2<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>28<\/strong><strong>\/0<\/strong><strong>4<\/strong><strong>\/2022<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><em>&#8211; Thi tuy\u1ec3n (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): <\/em>ng\u00e0y <strong>07,08\/05\/2022<\/strong>;<\/p>\n<p><em>&#8211; Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn)<\/em>: <strong>21<\/strong><strong>\/<\/strong><strong>05<\/strong><strong>\/202<\/strong><strong>2<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><em>3<strong>.2. L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp <\/strong>(t\u00f9y theo \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p):<\/em><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Li\u00ean th\u00f4ng l\u00ean cao \u0111\u1eb3ng: 1 <strong>&#8211;<\/strong> 1.5 n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Li\u00ean th\u00f4ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc: 1.5 <stro